    COUNT(DISTINCT usage_metadata["notebook_id"]) as notebooks,

from finops.system_lookups.v_system_usage_cost

datasets.name: bc8ecca7
datasets.query:
SELECT
    t1.workspace_id
    ,t1.job_id
    ,Last7DaySpend as `Last7Day$list`
    ,Last14DaySpend as `Last14Day$list`
    ,last7DaySpend - last14DaySpend as Last7DayGrowth
    ,try_divide( (last7DaySpend - last14DaySpend) , last14DaySpend) * 100 AS Last7DayGrowthPct
FROM
  (
    SELECT
      workspace_id,
      usage_metadata.job_id,
      SUM(est_total_cost) AS spend
      ,SUM(CASE WHEN usage_date BETWEEN date_add(current_date(), -8) AND date_add(current_date(), -1) THEN est_total_cost ELSE 0 END) AS Last7DaySpend
      ,SUM(CASE WHEN usage_date BETWEEN date_add(current_date(), -15) AND date_add(current_date(), -8) THEN est_total_cost ELSE 0 END) AS Last14DaySpend
    FROM finops.system_lookups.v_system_usage_cost
    GROUP BY ALL
  ) t1 
ORDER BY 
  Last7DayGrowth DESC 
LIMIT 100

SELECT
    *
    ,try_divide( (last30DaySpend - last30to60DaySpend) , last30to60DaySpend) * 100 AS Last30DayGrowth

      sum(est_total_cost) AS spend
      ,SUM(CASE WHEN usage_end_time BETWEEN date_add(current_date(), -30) AND current_date() THEN est_total_cost ELSE 0 END) AS Last30DaySpend

    FROM finops.system_lookups.v_system_usage_cost

  )

with billing_logs_with_list_cost as (
  SELECT
      t1.*, 
      t1.est_total_cost total_cost

datasets.name: 036341de
datasets.query:
-- SPENDING BROKEN DOWN BY JOB
with stats_per_job_run as (
  SELECT
    t1.workspace_id,
    t1.usage_metadata.job_id,
    t1.usage_metadata.job_run_id as run_id,
    SUM(t1.est_total_cost) as spend,
    first(identity_metadata.run_as, true) as run_as,
    first(t1.custom_tags, true) as custom_tags,
    MAX(t1.usage_end_time) as last_seen,
    MIN(t1.usage_start_time) as first_seen
  FROM  finops.system_lookups.v_system_usage_cost t1
  WHERE
      t1.usage_metadata.job_id IS NOT NULL
      AND t1.usage_metadata.job_run_id IS NOT NULL
      AND t1.usage_start_time >= CURRENT_DATE() - INTERVAL 30 DAY 
  GROUP BY 1,2,3
), 
stats_per_job AS (
  SELECT
    workspace_id,
    job_id,
    COUNT(run_id) AS runs,
    SUM(spend) AS total_spend,
    AVG(spend) AS avg_spend,
    MAX(spend) AS max_spend,
    percentile(spend, 0.9) AS p90
  FROM
    stats_per_job_run
  WHERE
    first_seen > CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() - INTERVAL 30 DAYS
  GROUP BY ALL
  ORDER BY total_spend DESC
)
SELECT
  *,
  (max_spend - p90) AS dbus_deviation_from_p90
FROM
  stats_per_job
ORDER BY
  dbus_deviation_from_p90 DESC

datasets.name: 9792ef05
datasets.query:
with serverless_logs as (
  SELECT
    t1.*
  FROM  finops.system_lookups.v_system_usage_cost t1
),
jobs_dollars as (
  select
    date_sub(to_date(usage_date), dayofweek(to_date(usage_date))) as week_start,
    SUM(est_total_cost) as spend,
    COUNT(distinct to_date(usage_start_time)) as days
  from
    serverless_logs t1 
  group by all
  having days = 7
  order by 1 asc, 2 asc
),
dbu_growth as (
    select
        week_start,
        spend,
        100 * (spend - lag(spend, 1) over (order by week_start)) / lag(spend, 1) over (order by week_start) as weekly_growth
    from jobs_dollars
    order by week_start asc
)
select
    week_start,
    weekly_growth,
    spend,
    avg(weekly_growth) over (order by week_start ROWS BETWEEN 12 preceding AND CURRENT ROW) as 3_months_growth_moving_avg
from dbu_growth
